Class BasicPID

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.usfirst.frc.team2791.robot.util.BasicPID

  • public class BasicPID
extends java.lang.Object
    This utility provides Basic PID based functions for any sort of control system. We used it in our PID based auto commands.
    Author:
    team2791: See Robot.java for contact info
